    <volume> 常用数据结构 </volume>
    <interface>BufferOf</interface>
    <method>IsNullOrEmpty </method>

    <description>
        <para>判断BufferOf数组或指向数组的指针是否为空。</para>
    </description>
    <syntax_nopara>
        <return_val>Boolean</return_val>
        <modifier>const</modifier>
        <NoArguments/>
    </syntax_nopara>

    <return>
        <para>BufferOf数组或指向数组的指针为空时，返回True，否则返回False。</para>
    </return>

<example>
<pre>
BufferOf&lt;Int8&gt; *MyArray = BufferOf&lt;Int8&gt;::Alloc(0);
CConsole::WriteLine(MyArray-&gt;IsNullOrEmpty());
BufferOf&lt;Int8&gt;::Free(MyArray);

BufferOf&lt;Int8&gt; MyArray1(NULL,0);
CConsole::WriteLine(MyArray1.IsNullOrEmpty());
</pre>
</example>    

